    public class HIScatter3d
extends HISeries
    /** A scatter3d series. If the type option is not specified, it is inherited from chart.type. scatter3d](#plotOptions.scatter3d). Configuration options for the series are given in three levels: 1. Options for all series in a chart are defined in the `plotOptions.series` object. 2. Options for all scatter3d series are defined in `plotOptions.scatter3d`. 3. Options for one single series are given in `the series instance array`. Highcharts.chart('container', { plotOptions: { series: { // general options for all series }, scatter3d: { // shared options for all scatter3d series } }, series: [{ // specific options for this series instance type: 'scatter3d' }] });
